{"tid":346531,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港比其他國家細,好應該變成單車城市啦","createTime":"2017-08-04T04:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T13:00:22.000Z","uid":122823,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"538568d3a6811e967dccf9021f3700d6ec432e6e","tid":346531,"uid":122823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:42:42.000Z","msg":"香港比其他國家細,好應該變成單車城市啦,又可以減少塞車,對環保又好,對身體又好<br />\n<br />\n成撚日見D肥婆話減肥,又話飲杯水都肥,一日都唔知食幾多磅肉,多D去踩單車做下運動啦,搭乜鬼車呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://spider.nosdn.127.net/3562271953cc435a78aaa30033dad2ac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fspider.nosdn.127.net%2F3562271953cc435a78aaa30033dad2ac.gif&h=444d010f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.kknews.cc/large/26e60001af4026a131af\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F26e60001af4026a131af&h=3d2ff0b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aff74e502da68073f12ea76e8e3513a4920f3e7f","tid":346531,"uid":39582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:43:18.000Z","msg":"正皮"},{"pid":"6c5961527cf1d5f0cb01e88ea1eecf121c9922c1","tid":346531,"uid":71864,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"九龍要砍掉重練"},{"pid":"eaf675185e48723511f5b68fdda7915862f4bff5","tid":346531,"uid":66044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:44:30.000Z","msg":"見到成堆單車徑斷開一截截咁就知政府唔會做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84fcb55bbcb4dd85ba6925d44feb886b798f2f46","tid":346531,"uid":80909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"咪係 荷蘭咁大個國家都可以單車全國通行"},{"pid":"ea124fb68ee752851cbba21b5718e7e91e2f2d3e","tid":346531,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"全球最短單車徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758d43973286e9b322e5fc12ac7cde2c8c4e7d68","tid":346531,